/* 
This do file runs the main event studies, but focues on those events whose post-event managers' average exposure is within range [15, 30].

Note:
    To avoid right-censoring, we focus only on workers with event time <= year 2019.

Input:
    "${TempData}/04MainOutcomesInEventStudies_EarlyAgeM.dta" <== constructed in 0104 do file.
    "${TempData}/temp_Mngr_Exposure.dta" <== constructed in 0702 do file.
    "${TempData}/temp_Mngr_Exposure_NonMovers.dta" <== constructed in 0703 do file.

RA: WWZ 
Time: 2024-11-01
*/

